{"parentUuid":"8496ecc5-bc6f-4ead-bd81-87da85bdb28a","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"53f5148a-6791-4be6-a2fc-f4eaf65be586","agentId":"aab619a6f776136ee","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LyyAbPEim36pFUYSp3bzUr","type":"tool_result","content":"101:   `prepare_export(principal, params)`, which runs a `COUNT(*)` with the same filters inside\n149:- `async def prepare_export(principal, params) -> None` — opens `scoped_transaction(\n169:    `completed`) — placed in `finally` so a client disconnect mid-stream still records what\n358:- `src/services/usage_export_service.py` — `prepare_export` (cap check) + `stream_export_csv`\n478:[Omitted long matching line]\n490:- **R3 — mid-stream failure truncates the CSV** rather than returning a clean error envelope: once\n492:  (oversized result) is caught cleanly by the pre-flight 422; a rare mid-stream DB error yields a\n508:        Cap(prepare_export: pre-flight count cap → 422)\n565:  error-envelope facade (no stack/SQL); filename is a UTC timestamp only; Cache-Control:"}]},"uuid":"0e2555f7-1dc6-4aec-9102-dca1c0368bcc","timestamp":"2026-07-09T17:46:18.330Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"8496ecc5-bc6f-4ead-bd81-87da85bdb28a","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"d6fd840f-4c15-4ec4-8e2b-f4a42b2cbb1a","version":"2.1.204","gitBranch":"feature/usage-export"}
